title: DevilDriver - Winter Kills Live in Berlin Bonus [MP3 Only]
description:
So, here a rip of the Live in Berlin bonus DVD that comes with Winter Kills Limited Edition.
As advertised by the band, the recording is raw as hell, so the somewhat "flawed" quality of it is not due to its rip.

Tracklist:

01 - End of The Line
02 - Dead to Rights
03 - Not All Who Wander Are Lost
04 - Pure Sincerity
05 - Head on to Heartache
06 - I Could Care Less
07 - The Mountain
08 - Clouds Over California
09 - Meet The Wretched

320kpbs, 44,100kHz.

Enjoy,
Daz.
